                  <p>Doing anything well requires preparation and this is especially true when serving a mutlilingual audience.</p><p>This is why we designed SPF.IO to be straightforward to use. You craft your message. Someone translates it. You deliver your message, with subtitles and slides appearing on a screen in sync with your speech. Your audience follows in their native language on their mobile devices. They can also take notes or give you feedback. Afterwards, you can review what they said and address it.</p>
